

Vagrantfile:
Vagrant.configure('2') do |config|

  config.vm.provider :linode do |provider, override|
    override.ssh.private_key_path = '~/.ssh/id_rsa'
    #override.vm.box = 'linode/ubuntu1404'
    #override.vm.box_url = "https://github.com/displague/vagrant-linode/raw/master/box/linode.box"
    config.vm.box = 'linode/ubuntu1404'

    provider.api_key = 'PDBQmEZf4jd4llBXVRkvEOKAIoYlkiqCu6D1EvecyGFaEoq0vDSuuCFuSr6SbrCd'
    provider.distribution = 'Ubuntu 14.04'
    provider.datacenter = 'fremont'
    provider.plan = 'Linode 1024'
    #provider.planid = 1
    # provider.planid = <int>
    # provider.paymentterm = <*1*,12,24>
    # provider.datacenterid = <int>
    # provider.image = <string>
    # provider.imageid = <int>
    # provider.kernel = <string>
    # provider.kernelid = <int>
    # provider.private_networking = <boolean>
    # provider.stackscript = <string> # Not Supported Yet
    # provider.stackscriptid = <int> # Not Supported Yet
    # provider.distributionid = <int>

    # Shell Scripts
    config.vm.provision :shell, path: "setup.sh"
    config.vm.provision :shell, path: "apache.sh"
  end
end


Get a list of Operating System images Linode provides.
    Command: vagrant linode distributions
          ==> default: ID   Size   Distribution Name
          ==> default: 60   950    CentOS 5.6
          ==> default: 78   550    Debian 6
          ==> default: 86   600    Slackware 13.37 32bit
          ==> default: 87   600    Slackware 13.37
          ==> default: 117  1000   Slackware 14.1
          ==> default: 118  3072   Gentoo 2013-11-26
          ==> default: 120  1024   openSUSE 13.1
          ==> default: 122  1536   Fedora 20
          ==> default: 124  750    Ubuntu 14.04 LTS
          ==> default: 126  550    Ubuntu 12.04 LTS
          ==> default: 127  675    CentOS 6.5
          ==> default: 129  750    CentOS 7
          ==> default: 130  600    Debian 7
          ==> default: 134  650    Fedora 21
          ==> default: 135  700    openSUSE 13.2
          ==> default: 137  2000   Gentoo 2014.12
          ==> default: 138  800    Arch Linux 2015.02
          ==> default: 139  1500   Ubuntu 15.04
          ==> default: 140  900    Debian 8.1
          ==> default: 141  650    Fedora 22
          ==> default: 142  800    Arch Linux 2015.08
          ==> default: 144  1500   Ubuntu 15.10

    Change distribution option after the equal sign provider.distribution = 'Ubuntu 14.04' to anything in the list above

Get a list of Datacenter locations
    Command: vagrant linode datacenters
          ==> default: Datacenter ID   Location                             Abbr
          ==> default: 2               Dallas, TX, USA                      dallas
          ==> default: 3               Fremont, CA, USA                     fremont
          ==> default: 4               Atlanta, GA, USA                     atlanta
          ==> default: 6               Newark, NJ, USA                      newark
          ==> default: 7               London, England, UK                  london
          ==> default: 8               Tokyo, JP                            tokyo
          ==> default: 9               Singapore, SG                        singapore
          ==> default: 10              Frankfurt, DE                        frankfurt
    Change the datacenter location(fremont) provider.datacenter = 'fremont' to anything from the list above, use the column labeled "Abbr"

Get a list of plans provided by Linode.
    Command: vagrant linode plans
          ==> default: Plan ID                              Plan Name
          ==> default: 1                                    Linode 1024
          ==> default: 2                                    Linode 2048
          ==> default: 4                                    Linode 4096
          ==> default: 6                                    Linode 8192
          ==> default: 7                                    Linode 16384
          ==> default: 8                                    Linode 32768
          ==> default: 9                                    Linode 49152
          ==> default: 10                                   Linode 65536
          ==> default: 12                                   Linode 98304

Get a list of Linodes status
    Command: vagrant linode servers
          ==> default: LinodeID Label                          DataCenter           Plan       Status
          ==> default: 16123    srv2                           3                    0          1
          ==> default: 320326   srv1                           4                    2          1

